Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:13.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:17.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:21.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:33.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:34.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:41.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then when the pass comes this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.57,0:01:44.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you head straight that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:48.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:49.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, this is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:51.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's going to try to block you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:54.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic, just kick it back a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:58.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to, like, picture how the game's going to unfold in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:01.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.76,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,They're pumped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sports day's coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:18.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your knees bent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:23.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then sort of grind the ball out with the inside of your foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:27.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And push! Push! Push! Push! Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:26.48,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:27.79,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Grind the ball out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:31.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:35.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:38.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:39.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:40.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:47.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:51.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't like her, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:53.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you tell, Yano-chin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:54.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're simple-minded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:58.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that it's a bad thing that Sadako has new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:02.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:04.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:08.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But seriously, I'd be so pissed if she became closer to her than to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:11.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're cute, Chizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:18.69,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a new friend again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:25.68,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, it's not like I put in any effort, so I don't know what to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:33.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:43.68,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is what it's like to make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:52.79,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't really hit me, but I still feel happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:03.97,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why did I just see Kazehaya-kun's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:07.01,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:11.28,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:21.74,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan's my friend now too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:26.91,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so blessed, yet I feel the opposite...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:40.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:43.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:50.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:51.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tension, you know, tension.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:59.23,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:06.19,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really talk to Kazehaya-kun too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:12.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:20.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:23.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to give you the committee form.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:24.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:25.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, the CD.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:29.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:32.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought it? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:39.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:40.74,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:49.03,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute, nice and friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:52.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:13.00,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan doesn't get nervous like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:17.31,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.30,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:20.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:22.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:29.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I surprised you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:37.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't notice me calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sorry for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:42.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:44.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:46.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ku—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:54.24,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I called her by name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that uncalled for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:00.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally called me Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:04.20,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It went alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:08.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to carry half?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:09.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:16.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Job? You're funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:20.04,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could be like Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:25.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the form, yo. Pass me the CD.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:27.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:29.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woohoo! Thanks dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:30.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,American?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:33.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:38.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:41.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can talk to me about it if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:44.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:47.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:53.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to me about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:08:02.47,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My role model wants to hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on pitcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:09.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitcher, pitch to contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:15.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a hard time talking to Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:20.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe boys and girls are too different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:22.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get too self-conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:25.02,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:31.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've known him since middle school, and my guess is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:36.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya's always been really nice to kids that don't fit in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:40.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He talks to anyone and everyone really casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:44.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I think he talks to you normally too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:46.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:52.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's not anything special that he talks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:56.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you need to get so tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:58.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:06.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then again, you're so different from Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:07.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:13.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe you'll have a better time talking to someone not as outgoing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:17.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:23.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, people get along with some people better than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:30.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:35.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's why you talk to him so casually.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:42.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sort of alike in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:44.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:51.23,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun was calling her by name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're close to him, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:10:00.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close to him? No, that's just normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:02.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normal? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:08.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? The standards are so high!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.85,0:10:18.55,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I see; if that's normal for Kurumi-chan, then no wonder I feel nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:21.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should head back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:23.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:26.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:31.52,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I could hardly even say “hi” to him at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And that used to be normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kurumi-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:55.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm more confident after I talked to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:01.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One step at a time. That's what I'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:04.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little nervous, but I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:06.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:07.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:08.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:14.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I could ever become like you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:18.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:21.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Forget I said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:39.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi's, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:44.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, back in middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:47.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:51.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumi-chan likes Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:54.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good friends with Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:56.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can help out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:12:00.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind being relied on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:04.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you just want me to make an opportunity for the two of you to be alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:05.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done and done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:08.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so helpful, Chizu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:14.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then she confessed to him and got rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:17.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was all fine and stuff, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:21.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan, can you help with her too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:27.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu-chan, it's her this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:32.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizu, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:35.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:41.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's another girl who wants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:43.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:51.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:52.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:55.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to help Yumi but not me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:57.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were on Yumi's side, Chizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:13:01.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.08,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chizu-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:02.25,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,why, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:03.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:06.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's not Chizu-chan's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:11.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good for the girls in our class to get split up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:19.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe no one should confess to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:28.87,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:32.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:35.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya belongs to all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:39.54,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god, that's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:48.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who was afraid of having him taken by someone else joined up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:56.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, she's not exactly a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:58.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I help her out; she helps me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:00.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:00.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like her type.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:02.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I don't want to hang out with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:06.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so being used.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:12.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of know what she's really like now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:19.92,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see if things really go as she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:22.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:25.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:27.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:29.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:32.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, buy me some tea too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:33.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:44.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I could ever become like you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:49.83,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I went a little too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.87,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:05.42,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:07.36,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:18.56,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, I called her name but now I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:21.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:24.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:28.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't talked to you in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:32.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:38.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just going to buy a drink and I saw you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:39.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:43.92,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, Kazehaya-kun was nervous too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:51.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:59.01,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun was thinking the same thing I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:08.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since we went to Ryu's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:16.40,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.01,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.01,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,You smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.53,0:16:23.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you smile in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:28.59,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:34.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Maru's pretty big now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:37.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:40.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so active.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:43.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He makes a mess inside the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:47.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to make him a doghouse soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:52.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maru-chan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to come visit him sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:05.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gets so lonely though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:09.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he'll stay put inside the doghouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:18.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.02,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:30.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:31.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:33.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:36.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name's Kurumizawa Ume.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:38.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumizawa Ume?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:40.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kurumizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:42.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:45.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumizawa Ume-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Kurumizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:57.34,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he wasn't calling her by name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:18:01.24,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumizawa Ume-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:02.85,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Ume-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:08.14,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm burning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:11.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:18.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya, can I borrow Sawako-chan for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:22.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:25.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk to her, girl to girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:29.66,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl to girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:36.23,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does someone always get in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:51.65,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what she wants to talk to me about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:59.15,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,How far are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:01.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kuru—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:09.62,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ume-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:11.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me Ume.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:18.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:20.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:23.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:25.54,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, a nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:31.01,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had crossed the line and made her angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:38.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, there's someone I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:42.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go out with him, but I don't think I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:45.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.09,0:19:48.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:53.08,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:56.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:59.82,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She needs my help, but I can't think of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:04.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I want you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:09.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Be of use to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:12.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Am I good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:15.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:18.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:24.20,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is the first time I've ever been so depended on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:26.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:28.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what exactly do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:36.18,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll tell you exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:42.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't I ruin the mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:45.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:47.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's someone you know well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:52.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:21:00.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya is the one I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.27,0:21:11.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.98,0:22:28.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncertain feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.01,0:22:30.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incomparable emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.29,0:22:34.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Special?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.04,0:22:36.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
